WEBVTT

00:01.068 --> 00:08.574
♪♪

00:08.576 --> 00:10.642
ZAK: There's a spirit
next door?

00:10.644 --> 00:12.845
It's a girl and a boy.

00:12.847 --> 00:17.049
This building saw a lot
of death of children.

00:17.051 --> 00:18.484
MAN: We're coming back.

00:18.486 --> 00:21.653
There is a news article
about a girl hanging herself.

00:21.655 --> 00:24.323
In another couple of hours,
he'd have been dead.

00:24.325 --> 00:25.991
The energy in here is crazy.

00:25.993 --> 00:28.026
Their spirits are here.

00:28.028 --> 00:30.195
-[Bleep]
-[ Laughing evilly ]

00:30.197 --> 00:31.330
BILLY: Who are you?

00:31.332 --> 00:38.570
♪♪

00:38.572 --> 00:40.305
ZAK:
There are things in this world

00:40.307 --> 00:42.341
that we will never
fully understand.

00:42.343 --> 00:43.842
[<i> Distorted</i> ]<i> Understand.</i>

00:43.844 --> 00:47.079
[ Echoing ] We want answers.

00:47.081 --> 00:53.218
We have worked years to build
our credibility, our reputation,

00:53.220 --> 00:57.423
working alongside
the most renowned professionals

00:57.425 --> 00:58.991
in the field,

00:58.993 --> 01:01.193
capturing groundbreaking proof
of the paranormal.

01:01.195 --> 01:03.462
It's working!

01:03.464 --> 01:05.531
I can't give you
an explanation.

01:05.533 --> 01:06.598
[ Birds cawing ]

01:06.600 --> 01:08.967
This is<i> our</i> evidence...

01:08.969 --> 01:11.236
our ghost adventures.

01:11.238 --> 01:16.575
♪♪

01:16.577 --> 01:18.844
We're in Saint Anthony, Idaho,

01:18.846 --> 01:21.914
at the Idaho
Industrial Reform School.

01:21.916 --> 01:24.583
This massive structure
behind me,

01:24.585 --> 01:26.485
this was the girls' wing.

01:26.487 --> 01:31.156
Children were sent here
against their will, broken,

01:31.158 --> 01:32.624
trying to be reformed,

01:32.626 --> 01:36.261
but there was no refuge
here for them at all.

01:36.263 --> 01:40.766
The conditions here were so bad

01:40.768 --> 01:44.503
that some of them chose
to take their own lives.

01:44.505 --> 01:48.774
On this very property,
there are 20 graves of children

01:48.776 --> 01:52.411
that died from
suspicious circumstances.

01:52.413 --> 01:57.082
The evil that occurred here
has created something dark,

01:57.084 --> 02:00.018
and the families that have tried
living in this building

02:00.020 --> 02:06.425
have lived in absolute misery
with never-ending disturbances.

02:06.427 --> 02:08.894
We're here to confront
whatever darkness

02:08.896 --> 02:11.597
was ignited
by the pure terror

02:11.599 --> 02:15.067
that was created by man
on these children.

02:15.069 --> 02:20.005
♪♪

02:20.007 --> 02:25.978
Founded in 1903, the Idaho
State Reform School

02:25.980 --> 02:29.014
was home to the region's
most wayward youth.

02:29.016 --> 02:31.917
♪♪

02:31.919 --> 02:34.653
Towards the end
of the 20th century,

02:34.655 --> 02:41.226
this former girls' dormitory and
infirmary were decommissioned

02:41.228 --> 02:43.996
and eventually sold
to various families

02:43.998 --> 02:47.032
who transformed them
into their homes,

02:47.034 --> 02:50.369
and it's our concern
that these past events

02:50.371 --> 02:51.803
have opened a doorway

02:51.805 --> 02:55.440
to something dark combined
with some other

02:55.442 --> 03:00.412
trapped spirits
with evil intentions.

03:00.414 --> 03:06.618
♪♪

03:06.620 --> 03:07.619
Barrett.
-Yeah.

03:07.621 --> 03:08.820
Demi, how you doing?

03:08.822 --> 03:10.255
Zak Bagans,
nice to meet you.

03:10.257 --> 03:11.757
-Nice to meet you.
-How you doing?

03:11.759 --> 03:14.927
So the history of this place
is pretty dark.

03:14.929 --> 03:16.595
-Yeah.
-Yes.

03:16.597 --> 03:19.197
Do you live
inside of this house?

03:19.199 --> 03:20.666
-Yes, we do.
-Yes, we do.

03:20.668 --> 03:24.870
Are the both of you
experiencing hauntings?

03:24.872 --> 03:27.539
-I've been bitten.
-You've been bitten?

03:27.541 --> 03:29.141
Yes, by one
of the spirits here.

03:29.143 --> 03:31.310
Okay.

03:31.312 --> 03:33.378
ZAK:
Because of this attack on Demi,

03:33.380 --> 03:34.813
we need to share something

03:34.815 --> 03:37.749
we witnessed prior
to the start of filming.

03:37.751 --> 03:38.717
-Oh, who saw it?
-I saw it.

03:38.719 --> 03:40.018
-You saw it.
-I saw it.

03:40.020 --> 03:42.354
-You saw it.
-That's where it was.

03:42.356 --> 03:45.357
When we arrived,
we got out of our car,

03:45.359 --> 03:47.159
bike is here on a kickstand,

03:47.161 --> 03:49.528
and this thing wasn't
just, like,

03:49.530 --> 03:54.032
oh, it just kind of
teetered over and hit this.

03:54.034 --> 03:55.601
It was like something grabbed it

03:55.603 --> 04:00.205
and literally threw it into
this wooden piece right here.

04:00.207 --> 04:01.306
Well, believe it or not,

04:01.308 --> 04:02.708
that tends to happen
all the time.

04:02.710 --> 04:05.143
Things are always, like,
knocking over and stuff.

04:05.145 --> 04:06.445
Whose bike is it?

04:06.447 --> 04:08.246
It's my little brother's,
Magnum.

04:08.248 --> 04:09.581
Does Magnum live here?

04:09.583 --> 04:10.916
Yes, he does.

04:10.918 --> 04:13.652
Okay, what is symbolic
with Magnum in this place?

04:13.654 --> 04:15.687
He's autistic.

04:15.689 --> 04:17.756
-He's autistic?
-Yeah.

04:17.758 --> 04:20.959
I've done research in the past
with a link

04:20.961 --> 04:24.763
with autism
and spirit interaction.

04:24.765 --> 04:28.533
Have you noticed anything
with your brother, Magnum,

04:28.535 --> 04:33.839
communicating or experiencing
any spirits inside of here?

04:33.841 --> 04:34.906
He got locked in one

04:34.908 --> 04:36.742
of the solitary-confinement
rooms once.

04:36.744 --> 04:38.110
-When?
-Really?

04:38.112 --> 04:39.544
This was a while back.

04:39.546 --> 04:41.747
He said that
the door just shut.

04:41.749 --> 04:44.916
♪♪

04:44.918 --> 04:46.885
Is there a way to ask him

04:46.887 --> 04:50.222
if there was anything
going on with him?

04:50.224 --> 04:53.659
If spirits in here are doing
things like that to him,

04:53.661 --> 04:56.428
I want to make sure
there's a spirit

04:56.430 --> 04:57.763
that's not upset with him.

04:57.765 --> 04:59.398
-Right.
-Okay.

04:59.400 --> 05:00.766
Hmm.

05:00.768 --> 05:02.968
My dad just went to get him,
so he...

05:02.970 --> 05:06.672
I think he'll come out
in just a minute.

05:06.674 --> 05:07.973
How you doing, man?

05:07.975 --> 05:09.608
-Doing good.
-Good, good.

05:09.610 --> 05:11.309
So I got a quick
question for you.

05:11.311 --> 05:12.844
Okay.

05:12.846 --> 05:16.548
Do you ever have any
experiences in here

05:16.550 --> 05:18.617
with the spirits or...

05:26.493 --> 05:28.994
And is it
a guy or a girl?

05:35.235 --> 05:37.769
Are there any spirits in here
that aren't nice?

05:42.609 --> 05:45.243
There's a spirit
next door?

05:49.249 --> 05:50.949
Why are they
not nice to you?

05:59.526 --> 06:01.860
These mean spirits,
they do come outside?

06:10.070 --> 06:12.571
When you took
your bike today,

06:12.573 --> 06:14.372
did you feel anything
when you were on your bike?

06:21.682 --> 06:24.349
The girl spirit that stays
in your room

06:24.351 --> 06:26.485
was just helping
you get your bike...
Yeah.

06:26.487 --> 06:28.220
...making sure that
they don't bother you?

06:28.222 --> 06:30.322
Mm-hmm.

06:30.324 --> 06:31.389
That's interesting.

06:31.391 --> 06:40.132
♪♪

06:40.134 --> 06:44.035
So after talking to your brother
and asking him

06:44.037 --> 06:47.906
about these experiences
and these spirits

06:47.908 --> 06:52.577
that he is interacting with,
is that new news to you?

06:52.579 --> 06:55.514
Yeah, about him being stopped
while he was trying to work

06:55.516 --> 06:58.150
and stuff,
that was huge.

06:58.152 --> 07:00.986
I had never heard any of that.

07:02.990 --> 07:07.325
Does that change anything
with him here?

07:07.327 --> 07:08.493
You mean, am I worried
about him?

07:08.495 --> 07:10.028
Yeah.

07:10.030 --> 07:12.864
A little bit, yeah.

07:12.866 --> 07:15.634
I mean, I'm definitely gonna
have to keep a closer eye on him

07:15.636 --> 07:17.435
and see what he's up to.

07:17.437 --> 07:22.541
♪♪

07:22.543 --> 07:24.976
Do you know of any
occurrences here

07:24.978 --> 07:28.413
that happened that would
cause a spirit

07:28.415 --> 07:31.650
to be at unrest
and aggravated?

07:31.652 --> 07:33.151
I know that there is
a news article

07:33.153 --> 07:35.487
about a girl hanging herself.

07:37.224 --> 07:40.659
It was in this building.

07:40.661 --> 07:41.793
That's documented?

07:41.795 --> 07:44.029
Yes, it's documented.

07:44.031 --> 07:45.964
ZAK: Due to the sudden
and violent manner

07:45.966 --> 07:48.767
in which this young
student named Hope died,

07:48.769 --> 07:51.803
we suspect something evil

07:51.805 --> 07:55.073
has manifested itself here
from all of the pain

07:55.075 --> 07:57.676
and suffering inflicted
on these children.

07:57.678 --> 08:00.512
What has happened
with you here?

08:00.514 --> 08:02.280
This hallway right over here,

08:02.282 --> 08:04.482
I used to live
in the room there.

08:04.484 --> 08:07.819
One night, when I was walking
down just to go to bed,

08:07.821 --> 08:10.055
there's the little windows
in the doors,

08:10.057 --> 08:14.292
and I just saw a face
pop up in the window.

08:14.294 --> 08:17.996
So I went in there and opened up
the door and walked around,

08:17.998 --> 08:20.298
and there was no one in there.

08:20.300 --> 08:22.968
I want you to tell me
about these bite marks.

08:22.970 --> 08:26.271
Well, it was when I first
permanently moved downstairs,

08:26.273 --> 08:27.973
and I was getting
ready for work,

08:27.975 --> 08:30.075
and I always feel like
I'm being followed.

08:30.077 --> 08:32.344
I was just minding
my own business,

08:32.346 --> 08:34.613
and then I looked down
at my arm.

08:34.615 --> 08:36.581
You could feel
the teeth marks,

08:36.583 --> 08:40.485
and they appeared
to be child-size teeth,

08:40.487 --> 08:42.053
just one right
next to the other.

08:42.055 --> 08:44.456
You could see
each tooth mark

08:44.458 --> 08:46.291
indented into your skin?

08:46.293 --> 08:48.560
-Yeah.
-That's pretty scary.

08:48.562 --> 08:52.697
So I'm a little
concerned now, honestly.

08:52.699 --> 08:54.332
Girl hung herself here.

08:54.334 --> 08:55.867
-Yes.
-Okay.

08:55.869 --> 08:58.503
You have bite marks
on your arm.

08:58.505 --> 09:02.674
You see a face in one
of the rooms at night.

09:02.676 --> 09:05.243
The two spirits over in the
other building, the infirmary,

09:05.245 --> 09:09.481
are the ones I'm concerned
about, a female and a male.

09:09.483 --> 09:11.182
Their spirits are here.

09:11.184 --> 09:15.353
♪♪

09:15.355 --> 09:18.657
ZAK: So far, a lot of things
have been happening here,

09:18.659 --> 09:22.193
and the most troubling part
about all of this

09:22.195 --> 09:27.365
and the most unnerving part is
we're dealing with all children.

09:27.367 --> 09:30.068
Behind me, in this
sinister-looking building,

09:30.070 --> 09:32.437
this was the infirmary.

09:32.439 --> 09:37.242
This building saw a lot
of death of children.

09:37.244 --> 09:40.979
On the property,
there's 22 marked graves.

09:40.981 --> 09:44.082
See, I'm pumped up because
when I'm dealing with children,

09:44.084 --> 09:45.350
and I know that
they were beaten,

09:45.352 --> 09:46.651
and they took their own lives

09:46.653 --> 09:48.420
from what they had
to go through here,

09:48.422 --> 09:50.288
you can feel that here.

09:50.290 --> 09:54.259
You could feel
all the emotion here.

09:54.261 --> 09:56.294
Man, it's tough.

09:56.296 --> 09:57.529
Me and my little sister

09:57.531 --> 09:59.531
would play
with the little girl here.

09:59.533 --> 10:01.933
They couldn't tell the
difference between spirit

10:01.935 --> 10:03.168
and flesh.

10:06.239 --> 10:08.939
♪♪

10:08.941 --> 10:12.543
ZAK: With a severe amount
of activity documented thus far

10:12.545 --> 10:15.713
at the Idaho State
Reform School,

10:15.715 --> 10:19.083
we shift our focus
from the former girls' dormitory

10:19.085 --> 10:21.619
to the now-defunct infirmary,

10:21.621 --> 10:25.089
which was once home
to another family.

10:25.091 --> 10:26.757
Hello.
Hi. I'm Zak.

10:26.759 --> 10:28.559
-I'm Shandy.
-Shandy.

10:28.561 --> 10:30.094
-Jamie.
-Jamie.

10:30.096 --> 10:32.830
-Aronley.
-Aronley, how you doing?

10:32.832 --> 10:37.201
So, um, you all three
used to live

10:37.203 --> 10:38.536
in the infirmary.
-Mm-hmm.

10:38.538 --> 10:40.037
-Yes.
-Mm-hmm.

10:40.039 --> 10:42.106
Are you related to the family
that's living here now?

10:42.108 --> 10:43.307
-No.
-No.

10:43.309 --> 10:45.643
When is the last time
you were in here?

10:45.645 --> 10:47.111
Second grade.

10:47.113 --> 10:48.813
15 years ago.

10:48.815 --> 10:51.248
Can someone give me
a quick respirator?

10:51.250 --> 10:54.318
I would like for you all
to take us in there

10:54.320 --> 10:58.355
and tell us
what you experienced.

11:00.026 --> 11:03.060
It was hard to make
this place a home.

11:03.062 --> 11:06.997
I really am pretty in-tune
to the spirit world,

11:06.999 --> 11:08.165
but, when we moved here,

11:08.167 --> 11:09.667
I had to turn
all of that off

11:09.669 --> 11:12.269
because I had little girls
I had to raise.

11:12.271 --> 11:14.972
♪♪

11:14.974 --> 11:17.241
Could you take me and tell me
what you experienced?

11:17.243 --> 11:19.743
Yeah.

11:19.745 --> 11:22.847
This was our bedroom.

11:22.849 --> 11:24.415
Me and my little sister
would play

11:24.417 --> 11:27.418
with the little girl
here all the time.

11:27.420 --> 11:28.752
♪ Ring around the rosie ♪

11:28.754 --> 11:29.820
They were our friends.

11:29.822 --> 11:31.021
♪ Pocketful of posies ♪

11:31.023 --> 11:33.424
We thought she was
the neighbor kid.

11:33.426 --> 11:35.426
We actually seen them
physically.

11:35.428 --> 11:38.295
-She was that vivid?
-Mm-hmm.

11:38.297 --> 11:40.898
♪ Ashes, ashes ♪

11:40.900 --> 11:43.200
♪ We all fall down ♪

11:43.202 --> 11:45.669
♪♪

11:45.671 --> 11:48.239
SHANDY: My sister was mean
as a child,

11:48.241 --> 11:49.940
and she locked me
in the cupboard,

11:49.942 --> 11:53.577
and the doctor untied it

11:53.579 --> 11:56.847
and helped me get out.

11:56.849 --> 11:59.149
So you lived with
a living doctor?

11:59.151 --> 12:00.818
The doctor was a ghost.

12:02.822 --> 12:04.588
He was an old man
with glasses,

12:04.590 --> 12:07.358
gray hair,
and a white jacket.

12:07.360 --> 12:12.963
♪♪

12:12.965 --> 12:15.099
Have you ever seen
the little girl

12:15.101 --> 12:17.334
that your daughters
were playing with?

12:17.336 --> 12:20.504
One time, I was standing
at the sink,

12:20.506 --> 12:22.139
and the ball was bouncing.

12:22.141 --> 12:25.109
[ Ball bouncing ]

12:25.111 --> 12:26.844
So I'm washing dishes here,

12:26.846 --> 12:30.381
and I hear balls bouncing
and bouncing and giggles.

12:30.383 --> 12:33.817
My girls
were just giggling.

12:33.819 --> 12:35.686
And I turned, and I said,
"Why are you laughing at me?"

12:35.688 --> 12:38.255
and they go,
"The girl is bouncing the ball,"

12:38.257 --> 12:41.358
and I said,
"What girl, a ghost?"

12:41.360 --> 12:43.761
"No, just the little girl
who comes and plays."

12:43.763 --> 12:45.763
They thought she was real,
and they couldn't tell

12:45.765 --> 12:48.966
the difference
between spirit and flesh.

12:48.968 --> 12:51.468
♪♪

12:51.470 --> 12:54.138
Did you play
with the little girl,

12:54.140 --> 12:56.507
the spirit of the ghost
of the little girl?

12:56.509 --> 12:57.875
Yes.

12:57.877 --> 13:00.144
ZAK: Could the spirit
Shandy and her sister

13:00.146 --> 13:03.047
so vividly encountered
in their youth

13:03.049 --> 13:06.984
be that of Hope Chacon,
who, in the 1940s,

13:06.986 --> 13:10.087
hanged herself in
the girls' dormitory next door

13:10.089 --> 13:13.524
and who Magnum claims
now lives in his room?

13:22.335 --> 13:26.804
And with time passed since
the Gould family lived here,

13:26.806 --> 13:29.373
we also wonder
about the identities

13:29.375 --> 13:31.575
of the malevolent boy
and girl spirit

13:31.577 --> 13:35.713
who Magnum told us reside in
and around the infirmary.

13:35.715 --> 13:36.780
There's a spirit
next door?

13:39.685 --> 13:42.553
Shandy,
could you come here?

13:42.555 --> 13:44.221
We're going to see

13:44.223 --> 13:47.224
if you can communicate
with her.

13:49.261 --> 13:50.728
SHANDY: You want to come
out and play?

13:50.730 --> 13:52.563
[ Static ]

13:55.067 --> 13:56.433
Do you remember me?

13:56.435 --> 13:59.069
[ Static continues ]

13:59.071 --> 14:00.204
Can you do something

14:00.206 --> 14:03.407
