you're here with us?

14:03.409 --> 14:06.143
[<i> Indistinct voice</i> ]

14:06.145 --> 14:08.245
ZAK: What was that?

14:08.247 --> 14:10.314
Is that the doctor?

14:10.316 --> 14:11.982
We're sorry that we left.

14:11.984 --> 14:14.551
[<i> Indistinct voice</i> ]

14:14.553 --> 14:17.287
Whoa.
What was that?

14:18.791 --> 14:19.923
Can you do something

14:19.925 --> 14:24.061
and show us
that you're here?

14:24.063 --> 14:25.462
[<i> Indistinct voice</i> ]

14:28.467 --> 14:30.367
ZAK: And at the very moment

14:30.369 --> 14:33.904
this burst of activity
comes through the Spirit Box,

14:33.906 --> 14:38.375
our communication session is
interrupted by one of our crew

14:38.377 --> 14:42.346
who is startled by the sudden
presence of something unnerving.

14:42.348 --> 14:44.581
Bacon, come here.
Come here.

14:44.583 --> 14:47.051
I need you to tell
the camera this.

14:47.053 --> 14:48.385
Somebody punched
the car window,

14:48.387 --> 14:49.586
so I rolled
the windows down

14:49.588 --> 14:51.221
thinking someone
was gonna say something,

14:51.223 --> 14:53.257
and then no one did,
so I got out with my flashlight.

14:53.259 --> 14:56.160
I went around the car,
and then nobody was there.

14:56.162 --> 14:57.394
How hard was the punch?

14:57.396 --> 14:59.496
Like, a solid punch
to the passenger side.

14:59.498 --> 15:00.798
How long ago?

15:00.800 --> 15:02.399
Two minutes ago.

15:02.401 --> 15:06.270
The extreme poltergeist nature
of this encounter

15:06.272 --> 15:08.105
seems to mimic
what we witnessed

15:08.107 --> 15:12.242
at the very beginning
of our investigation.

15:12.244 --> 15:13.811
It was like something grabbed it

15:13.813 --> 15:17.281
and literally threw it into
this wooden piece right here.

15:17.283 --> 15:18.749
That tends to happen
all the time.

15:18.751 --> 15:21.151
Things are always, like,
knocking over and stuff.

15:21.153 --> 15:23.854
Stuff is happening
outside, too.

15:23.856 --> 15:25.923
-Yeah.
-Like, that's the crazy part is,

15:25.925 --> 15:27.558
like, it's bound
to the property.

15:27.560 --> 15:30.494
If it could punch this hard,
it could push a bike.

15:30.496 --> 15:33.864
Yeah.

